error: `prefer = ...` cannot be combined with `unwrap_in_r` on a function returning `Result<T, E>`: `unwrap_in_r` converts the whole `Result<T, E>` via a single `IntoR` impl (a tagged list for R to decode), not the inner `T` alone, so there is no plain `T` for `prefer=` to wrap. Remove `prefer=`.
